## Configuration

The service is configured via environment variables (prefix: `APP_`):

| Variable   | Default     | Description  |
|------------|-------------|--------------|
| `APP_HOST` | `0.0.0.0`   | Bind address |
| `APP_PORT` | `8080`      | Listen port  |

